info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.task

Class FinishedTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.task.FinishedTask

  • @Entity
public class FinishedTask
extends Object
    When a player has completed a Task, it will be added to the player’s list of finished tasks. At the same time the date is also stored when this request was sent and the task was officially be done. If the task is the last one to fulfill a goal, the goal is also added to the player’s list of finished goals and the player will obtain all its associated rewards.
